.SS timer
.IX Subsection "timer"
Returns the timer object.
.SS backend
.IX Subsection "backend"
Returns the reactor backend object.
.SS backend_name
.IX Subsection "backend_name"
Returns the backend name.
.SS sched
.IX Subsection "sched"
Returns the internal scheduler object.
